items.headline: Welcome to the Class of the Titans
items.desc: This is the Class of the Titans wikia. It has all 52 episodes, 2 seasons, and you can read and help write about 60 characters. We also have places, cities and groups, as well as pages for Greek mythology! We want this to be detailed as possible. Look though the homepage and see everything we are offering. Check out the 'Characters' pace to see who we have.
